description: The 2026 Nissan Rogue SV AWD is a fresh arrival in the automotive market, beautifully crafted and designed for those who appreciate modern technology, sleek aesthetics, and the versatility of an SUV. Its elegant White Pearl exterior exudes sophistication while offering the complete package of style and performance. Step inside and you'll be greeted by a Charcoal interior that provides a comfortable and stylish environment. The spacious cabin offers ample room for both passengers and cargo, making every journey a pleasant experience, whether it's a quick city drive or a long road trip. Under the hood, this Rogue features a 1.5L DOHC engine paired with a CVT with Xtronic transmission, offering smooth and efficient driving dynamics. The All-Wheel Drive (AWD) system ensures that you're ready for any road conditions, providing enhanced traction and stability.Enjoy the following features that enhance your driving experience:- **Advanced Safety Features**: Cruise with confidence thanks to a range of safety technologies designed to keep you and your passengers safe.- **Fuel Efficiency**: With an estimated 28 city MPG and 35 highway MPG, the Rogue SV is designed to be both eco-friendly and economical, helping you go further with less.- **Technology and Connectivity**: Stay connected on the go with intuitive infotainment systems, ensuring you have access to navigation, music, and more at your fingertips.- **Comfort and Convenience**: Experience the luxuries of premium seating and climate control, making every drive enjoyable regardless of the weather outside.With only 5 miles on the odometer, this brand-new SUV is ready to be taken on new adventures. It embodies the perfect blend of practicality, style, and cutting-edge technology, making it an ideal choice for families and individuals alike. For more information or to schedule a test drive, feel free to call at the provided contact number. Discover what makes the 2026 Nissan Rogue SV a standout option in the SUV category.
